learning_outcomes.en:
Upon completion of the course, participants:
1.	know how to use main databases of world languages /Ethnologue, WALS);
2.	know what is meant by the different bases of categorizing langauges and alo critics;  
3.	and how these categories is used depending on different aims of a research;
4.	know how to write Wikipedia entry and how to use sources for that.
